  <brief_title>To Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety Aliviador Compared to Gelol in Patients With Contusions, Sprains, Trauma and Muscle Injury.</brief_title>
  <acronym>LBB-ALI-01/09</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety Aliviador Compared to Gelol in the Relief in Patients With Contusons, Sprains,Trauma and Muscle Injury.</official_title>
