  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multicenter, randomized, double-blind trial, to evaluate the efficacy and safety Aliviador
      compared to Gelol in the relief of signs and symptoms in patients with contusions, sprains,
      trauma and muscle injury start with less than 24 hours or patients of myalgia, myofascial
      pain and tendinitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
